<p>Every time your two favorite geeks get together, something interesting happens: everyone learns at least five (5!) new things. This week&#039;s topics include two very specific features of APFS (a pro and a con), noise-canceling headphones for travel, a solution to drives not appearing on your Desktop, some Cool Stuff Found, and much, much more. Press play or download and enjoy!Note: Shownotes are complete!</p>
